title: Did Ari Fleischer compare his identity to be refined by voter identification laws?
subtitle: The tweeting of the former White House press secretary of apples to Orange Garnett is unrelated.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: The former White House Press Secretary, Ari Fletcher, said that showing identity when a COVID-19 vaccine was obtained in New York was "feeling" just like the voter identification laws that Republican legislators pressured.
